name: Clouds 004, 2020
description:
Clouds 004 (2020) is a part of Ruang Antara (The In-Between) body of work.

Clouds consists of 16 screenshots taken between 2020 - 2021, documenting Indonesia government initial response to pandemic and the social unrest. 

Digital Photo. JPEG | 6000x6000 | 300 DPI
